~~emerges after distress, prosperity follows adversity, and hardship is
~~followed by ease". commentary: 1. no one has the power to change the
~~decision of allah. 2. whatever trouble one has to suffer in this world,
~~it does not last for ever. every trouble is followed by prosperity,
~~pleasure and happiness. 3. one should never ask other than allah
~~anyone's help in supernatural way because it amounts to ascribing
~~partnership with allah. if a person is mindful of the rights of allah,
~~then allah, in return takes care of his needs and helps him.
