~~to bed, perform the salat wudu', lie down on your right side and say
~~[the above du`a (supplication)] and let these words be your last".
~~commentary: it is better to make wudu' before going to sleep. similarly,
~~it is also meritorious to recite the invocation mentioned in the hadith
~~before one goes to bed, because it is a prayer for the renewal of islam
~~and faith and request for grant of peace and security. PageV01P0096

