~~(pbuh) said, "jannah is nearer to anyone of you than your shoe-lace, and
~~so is the (hell) fire". [al-bukhari]. commentary: going to jannah or
~~hell is the result of one's own actions, both are close to everyone. one
~~will be admitted into jannah if he does good deeds, and will be
~~consigned to hell if he does evil. after death, one's entitlement for
~~jannah or hell will be decided. PageV01P0129

