~~impossible for him to sit, stand, lie, move and make use of different
~~organs of his body. thus every joint is a blessing for which one must
~~express gratitude to allah. it is yet another blessing of allah that he
~~has also told man a very easy way of thanksgiving which can be practised
~~even by the poorest man in the world. this means of thanksgiving is
~~recitation of tasbih (subhan allah), tahmid (al-hamdu lillah), takbir
