~~following three points: 1. the horror of the day of resurrection when
~~one will have to stand before allah to account for all his actions which
~~will then be lying at his both hands. 2. everyone should spend
~~according to his capacity in the way of allah in the form of sadaqah and
~~alms. in this way, good manners like polite conversation, etc., can also
~~become a means of his salvation. 3. one's actions alone would help him
~~on the day of resurrection. PageV01P0167

