~~faith". [muslim]. commentary: this hadith contains a very important
~~prescription to prevent the muslim society from all things which are
~~forbidden in islam. so long as muslims adhered to it and ceaselessly and
~~fearlessly performed their obligation of enjoining the right and
~~forbidding the wrong, their society was largely safe from many evils and
~~sins. PageV01P0232

