~~ظاهرا لا يحتمل تأويلا 186. `ubadah bin as-samit (may allah be pleased
~~with him) reported: we swore allegiance to messenger of allah (pbuh) to
~~hear and obey; in time of difficulty and in prosperity, in hardship and
