~~earth. the year consists of twelve months of which four are inviolable;
~~three of them consecutive - dhul-qa`dah, dhul-hijjah and muharram and
~~rajab, the month of mudar (tribe), which comes between jumada and
~~sha`ban. what month is this?'' we said, "allah and his messenger (pbuh)
