~~الجموع المنوع . وقيل : الضخم المختال في مشيته . وقيل : القصير البطين
~~252. harithah bin wahb (may allah be pleased with him) reported: i heard
~~messenger of allah (pbuh) saying, "shall i not inform you about the
~~people of jannah? it is every person who is, modest and humble (before
