~~companions of the prophet (pbuh) made for attaining a higher status in
~~virtue. 2. to spend the best of one's property in the way of allah is a
~~sign of perfection of faith. 3. in the matter of sadaqat (alms giving
~~and charity), preference must be given to one's closest relations,
~~provided they are poor and stand in need of help, otherwise, these
~~should be spent on other deserving people. PageV01P0372

