# وعن ابن عمر وعائشة رضي الله عنهما قالا قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه و
~~سلم : [ ما زال جبريل يوصيني بالجار حتى ظننت أنه سيورثه ] متفق عليه 303.
~~ibn `umar and `aishah (may allah be pleased with them) reported:
~~messenger of allah (pbuh) said, "jibril kept recommending treating
~~neighbours with kindness until i thought he would assign a share of
~~inheritance". [al-bukhari and muslim]. commentary: this hadith
~~illustrates the importance of nice treatment to neighbours in islam.
