~~such persons were his near relatives, he did not have any affection and
~~friendship with them because there cannot be any affection between a
~~pagan and a muslim. friendship and affection can only be for allah and
~~those who have faith in him. one can accommodate the non-muslim
~~relatives to the extent permitted by "maintaining the ties of kinship'',
~~provided they are not at war with the muslims. PageV01P0411

