~~she finally found her baby. she took the baby and hugged him". it is
~~permissible to illustrate by example what one cannot make others
~~understand by means of reason and senses, the way the prophet (pbuh) did
~~it in the present case. since it was not possible to describe the
~~immensity of allah's mercy, he cited the example of that woman to
