~~displease you". [muslim]. commentary: this hadith makes two points
~~clear: firstly, the kindness and mercy which the prophet (pbuh) had for
~~his ummah, a full manifestation of which will be seen on the day of
~~resurrection. secondly, the love that allah has for his prophet,
~~muhammad (pbuh). both these benefits will then go to the advantage of
~~the faithful muslims as they will be then blessed with mercy and
