~~attain, and for which one violates the injunctions of shari`ah, will be
~~forgotten with a glimpse of the hell-fire. therefore, the sensible
~~course is that one should adopt a way of life which is full of true
~~faith and good deeds so that one becomes eligible for the eternal
~~blessings and joys of the life of the hereafter. PageV01P0572

