# وعن أبي محمد فضالة بن عبيد الأنصاري رضي الله عنه أنه سمع رسول الله
~~صلى الله عليه و سلم يقول : [ طوبى لمن هدي للإسلام وكان عيشه كفافا وقنع ]
~~رواه الترمذي وقال حديث حسن صحيح 513. fadalah bin `ubaid al-ansari (may
~~allah be pleased with him) reported: i heard messenger of allah (pbuh)
~~say: "happiness is due to him who is guided to islam and possesses
~~provision that suffices him for his day and remains content.'' [at-
~~tirmidhi]. commentary: the word tuba (translated here as happiness) is
~~given to jannah. some ahadith say that it is the name of a heavenly tree
~~as well. lexically, however, it means greeting and good tiding. the
~~sense of this hadith is analogous to that of the previous one.
~~PageV01P0625

