~~muslim]. commentary: man constantly remains engaged in hoarding wealth
~~and there comes no point of termination to this process. rather, the
~~more he gets it, the more he is overpowered by lust for it till he is
~~carried to the grave. if man gets wealth in a dignified way without
~~being crazy for it, ethics certainly allows him to do so. PageV01P0638

