~~mercilessly. as a result of which the timid animals get upon one
~~another. in the hadith, this word has been brought in for a tyrant ruler
~~who subjects people to oppression and treats them unkindly. it implies a
~~strong warning and intimidation to cruel rulers PageV01P0812

