~~will render them guilty with allah. the prophet (pbuh) dissuades such
~~people from accepting any government portfolio as in this way they will
~~remain safe and trouble-free. yet, if a deserving person gets a job of
~~high responsibility, he should do his utmost to do full justice to it,
~~so that he may be spared remorse on the day of resurrection.
