~~769. ibn `umar (may allah be pleased with them) reported: during the
~~lifetime of messenger of allah (pbuh) we would eat while walking and
~~would drink while standing. [at-tirmidhi]. commentary: the companions
~~would not habitually eat something while being on the move and drink
~~water in a standing position. in fact, the hadith simply tells us that
