~~of allah (pbuh) saying, "silk (clothes) are worn only by him who has no
~~share in the hereafter.'' [al-bukhari and muslim]. commentary: this
~~hadith tells us that men will fall into a serious error if they wear
~~dress made from silk. and if they do not sincerely repent for it, they
