~~`alaikum wa rahmatullah (may you be safe from evil, and mercy of allah
~~be upon you).'' messenger of allah (pbuh) responded to his greeting and
~~the man sat down. messenger of allah (pbuh) said, "twenty.'' a third one
~~came and said: "as-salamu `alaikum wa rahmatullahi wa barakatuhu (may
~~you be safe from evil, and the mercy of allah and his blessings be upon
