~~a blessing both to you and to your family.'' [at-tirmidhi]. commentary:
~~many people, on returning home, feel belittled in saying as-salamu
~~`alaikum to their household. in fact, as-salam is a prayer for goodness,
~~blessing and peace, and one should have no complex about it.
