### || AUT 136 - باب السلام على الصبيان
# chapter 136 greeting the children PageV01P1102

### ||| AUT 862 -
# عن أنس رضي الله عنه أنه مر على صبيان فسلم عليهم وقال : كان رسول الله
~~صلى الله عليه و سلم يفعله . متفق عليه 862. anas (may allah be pleased
~~with him) reported that he passed by some children and greeted them.
~~then he said: "messenger of allah (pbuh) used to do the same.'' [al-
~~bukhari and muslim]. commentary: by greeting children, we please their
~~hearts and also vent our modesty. besides, the importance of as-salam is
~~unconsciously felt by them. above all it is the sunnah of the messenger
~~of allah (pbuh) and so we are supposed to put it into practice.
~~PageV01P1103

