~~qur'an (whole or part thereof) to memory (huffaz). the word `ascend'
~~here means to rise in ranks in the jannah. the more one remembers the
~~qur'an, the more clear and distinct is his recitation of it, the higher
~~would be the status that he will go on attaining through its blessings.
~~thus, this hadith provides inducement for the remembrance of the qur'an
