~~(pbuh) said, "o banu salamah! stay in your houses, because your
~~footprints (when you come to the mosque) will be recorded.'' he said
~~this twice. they said: "we would not have liked it, had we moved near
~~the mosque.'' [muslim]. commentary: this hadith mentions the merit of
