~~1.emphasis on performing salat in congregation. 2.the passion of the
~~companions of the prophet (pbuh) for salat. 3.evasion from salat with
~~congregation is a practice of hypocrites. 4.inducement for following the
~~sunnah of the prophet (pbuh) because evasion from it is bound to lead
~~one astray. PageV01P1377

