~~allah (pbuh) was asked: "which salat is the best?'' he replied, '' the
~~best salat is that in which qiyam (the duration of standing) is
~~longer.'' [muslim]. commentary: we learn from this hadith that of all
~~the articles of salat (ruku`, sujud, etc.), it is best to lengthen the
~~qiyam because the greater the qiyam is, the longer the recitation of the
~~qur'an will be. since the recitation of the qur'an is the best form of
~~remembrance of allah, the lengthening of the qiyam is also most
~~meritorious. PageV01P1510

