~~observing saum (fasting) for the whole month (except of the month of
~~ramadan) is disapproved. the model set by the prophet (pbuh) is the
~~ideal pattern of moderation in this respect. in this hadith the fasting
~~and the prayer of prophet dawud have been regarded most pleasing to
~~allah, because their conduct had a moderation which is enjoined by
~~islam. PageV01P1511

