~~he used to pray for the forgiveness of his shortcomings out of his
~~gratitude to allah's might and majesty. thus, this hadith has a great
~~lesson for us. in spite of being innocent, he was always fearful of the
~~wrath of allah, while we, despite being embodiments of sins, are
~~fearless of allah. PageV01P1815

