~~daji`u; wa a`udhu bika minal-khiyanati, fa-innaha bi'satil-bitanah' [o
~~allah! i seek refuge in you from hunger; surely, it is the worst
~~companion. and i seek refuge in you from treachery; surely, it is a bad
