~~her eye sight and cause her to die in her land.'' `urwah said: "she did
~~not die till she became blind. while she was walking in her land
~~(concerning which the dispute arose) she fell down into a pit and
~~died.'' [al-bukhari and muslim]. in another narration of muslim,
~~muhammad bin zaid bin `abdullah bin `umar said that he had seen arwa
