~~without thinking about its being good or not) and, as a result of this,
~~he will fall down into the fire of hell deeper than the distance between
~~the east and the west.'' [al-bukhari and muslim]. commentary: this
~~hadith shows the disadvantages which can be caused by the improper use
~~of the tongue. it is, therefore, essential that one should think before
~~he speaks. PageV01P1920

