~~the messenger of allah (pbuh), "how can salvation be achieved?'' he
~~replied, "control your tongue, keep to your house, and weep over your
~~sins.'' [at-tirmidhi]. commentary: it is better for one to spends his
~~surplus time at home in the remembrance of allah, the recitation of the
~~qur'an and the performance of acts of obedience, if one feels unable to
