~~this hadith were hypocrites (i.e., they revealed faith and concealed
~~disbelief). commentary: hypocrites are also people of mischievous and
~~doubtful conduct. it is, therefore, not only permissible but necessary
~~to make people aware of their real position so that people become
~~cautious about them and their religious and worldly life may remain safe
