~~said: i heard the messenger of allah (pbuh) saying, "if you find faults
~~with muslims, you will corrupt them.'' [abu dawud]. commentary: if a
~~muslim looks for the defects of another and hunts for his weaknesses,
~~other muslims will also adopt the same attitude towards him, and this
~~situation will create dissension and conflict in society. this also will
~~make them fall prey to sins and make them persistent in committing them.
~~for this reason, spying and finding faults with muslims has been
~~prohibited by shari`ah. PageV01P2011

