~~he, is of vast forgiveness. they do not realize that if allah so wills,
~~he can destroy all their deeds and consign them to hell and send the
~~other people who have been disparaged and underestimated to jannah.
~~therefore, one should never become proud of his piety nor should one
~~consider others of little value or good deeds, as only allah alone knows
~~what is inside our hearts. PageV01P2020

