~~repayment of a debt due to any of you is undertaken by a rich person,
~~you should agree to the substitution.'' [al-bukhari and muslim].
~~commentary: 1. evasion or procrastination in the payment of debt, when a
~~person is in a position to make its payment immediately, is prohibited.
~~2. if for the settlement of dispute, a rich man is entrusted to the
~~lender for recovery of his debt, the lender should accept this decision.
~~thus, this hadith induces one for an amicable way of settling disputes.
