~~heard the messenger of allah (pbuh) saying, "he who allows (others) to
~~wail over his death, will be punished for it on the day of
~~resurrection.'' [al-bukhari and muslim]. commentary: the torment
~~mentioned in this hadith will be inflicted on the day of judgement upon
~~that person who willed his heirs to wail on his death or who had brought
~~up his family in such a manner that they were apt to wail about the
~~death of their close relatives. PageV01P2150

