~~prophet (pbuh) has stated about the evil and sinfulness of showing off
~~implies that it is also a (minor) shirk. for instance he stated that "he
~~who kept fast or offered salat for mere show, has indeed committed
~~shirk.'' in any case, to take oath of anyone other than allah is
~~strictly forbidden. it is, therefore, necessary to abstain from swearing
~~by other than allah. unfortunately, such oaths are very common and
~~people do not realize that they are prohibited and unlawful.
