~~said: the messenger of allah (pbuh) forbade urinating into stagnant
~~water. [muslim]. commentary: "stagnant water'' means water which is not
~~flowing, like the water in a pond or a tank. when urination is
~~prohibited at such places, defecating would be more sternly prohibited.
