~~the practice of najsh (i.e., offering a high price for something in
~~order to allure another customer who is interested in the thing); and
~~that a man should make an offer while the offer of his brother is
~~pending; or that he should make a proposal of marriage while that of his
~~brother is pending; or that a woman should try that a sister of hers
