~~(pbuh) said, "avoid the seven destructive things.'' it was asked: (by
~~those present): "what are they, o messenger of allah?'' he replied,
~~"associating anyone or anything with allah in worship; practising
~~sorcery, killing of someone without a just cause whom allah has
~~forbidden, devouring the property of an orphan, eating of usury, fleeing
