# وعن عبد الله بن عمرو بن العاص رضي الله عنهما قال : رأى النبي صلى الله
~~عليه و سلم علي ثوبين معصفرين فقال : [ أمك أمرتك بهذا ؟ ] قلت : أغسلهما ؟
~~قال : [ بل أحرقهما ] وفي رواية : [ إن هذه من ثياب الكفار فلا تلبسها ]
~~رواه مسلم 1799. `abdullah bin `amr bin al-`as (may allah be pleased with
~~them) said: the prophet (pbuh) saw me dressed in two saffron-coloured
~~garments and asked, "has your mother commanded you to wear these?'' i
~~asked him, "shall i wash them out?'' he replied, "you had better set
~~them to fire.'' another narration is: "these are garments of the
~~disbelievers. so do not wear them.'' [muslim]. commentary: saffron and
~~safflower are plants with a bright orange-yellow colour. their use is
~~forbidden because this colour is generally used by women and
~~disbelievers, and men should show no resemblance to women and
~~disbelievers in their dress. PageV01P2359

